videos.description: Down three with the clock winding down, Arizona State's Kodi Justice banks in the 3-pointer, the Sun Devil's 12th basket from behind the arc, to send their game with Washington into overtime.
videos.headline: Justice sends game to OT with banked-in 3-pointer
